JsonReadIsItemUntilTouch
/ `(object,json)` → `(item,json)`: a json value narrows to dict so `%x.field%`
/ navigates it at runtime. There is no enduring PLang `object` type — item is both
/ the apex and the un-narrowed type. (The `is item`/`is dict` apex contract is
/ pinned in C# ItemApexTests; this goal proves the end-to-end narrow + navigation.)
- set %x% = {"field": 42}
- set %field% = %x.field%
- assert %field% equals 42
